    "The rest of the paper is organized as follows: Section II describe the search strategy and criteria used to identify 145 relevant literature, Section III reviews the existing methods, Section IV presents and discuss on the contribution and limitations leading to a set of conclusions in section V. II.",
    "This study utilized a comprehensive systematic literature review to gain a thorough understanding of the application of Deep Learning in snow hydrology parameter estimation.",
